-- SP-3.1: Refactor Plans CRUD — add features, seat_limit, usage_limits to plans.
-- ponytail: migration idempotent; extends P8.1 plan builder schema without breaking existing RPCs.

-- ============================================================
-- 1. Add new columns to public.plans
